dave_cheney.bio:
David is an open source contributor and project member for the Go programming language. David is a well-respected voice within the tech community, speaking on a variety of topics such as software design, performance, and the Go programming language.
In 2009, while idly perusing Google Reader (weâ€™ll never forget!) he ran across the announcement of a new open source language, Go. It was love at first sight. From that point Davidâ€™s passion has taken him around the world writing, teaching, and speaking about Go.
